# Supermart Grocery Sales Retail Analysis

## Dashboard Preview

![Dashboard](Mini%20Project%201%20Power%20Bi%20dashboard.png)

## Project Overview
This Power BI project analyzes grocery retail sales performance across regions, categories, and cities.

## Tools Used
- Power BI Desktop
- Power Query
- DAX

## Key Metrics
- Total Sales: 13.69M
- Total Profit: 3.43M
- Total Orders: 9153
- Profit Margin: 25%

## Charts Used
- Sales by Region
- Profit by Subcategory
- Sales by Month
- Sales by Category
- Orders by City

## Key Insights
- West region has the highest sales.
- Soft Drinks generate the highest profit.
- Sales peak during October–December.
- Kanyakumari has the highest number of orders.

